{"title":"上舰第一夜","authors":["曹奔"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上舰第一夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹奔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我睡在吊铺上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战舰好像摇篮把我轻轻摇晃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的思想插上翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海阔天空到处飞翔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听一听四周的声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友的鼾声亲切又甜香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮机的奏鸣使我陶醉神往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不禁打开了舷窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看一看海上的景况，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花闪烁着银色的月光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波浪在纵声歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不禁把飞溅的浪花接在手上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！滚滚的波浪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你把我满腔衷肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带给亲爱的人民："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个新水兵心里充满自豪和荣光。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}